'''''Xucphra Alazhi''''' was one of three [[Bacta Tanker]]s hijacked by [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] from a small convoy escorted by the [[Victory II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Victory II-class Star Destroyer]] [[Corrupter/Legends|''Corrupter'']] during the [[Ambush of the bacta tankers]]. It surrendered only after having lost its turbolasers, but was destroyed by the ''Corrupter'' while running on its exit vector from the system.

This ship was named after the [[Alazhi/Legends|Alazhi]], a key component of [[Bacta/Legends|bacta]]

